General:
    this is a simple function that take a text file with a list of dots
     and plot the circle the best fit the data.

 Input file format:
    each line of the file reprisents one point.
    the format of a line shold be:
        <x value>,<y value>

Algorithm:
    we use a basic linear regression approch.
    we change the ALPHA based on the data.